# Expert QA after changes

After you finish a meaningful change to this project (HTML/JS/CSS, auth, legal, lessons, deploy config):

1. Read and follow `.cursor/skills/englishpath-qa-tester/SKILL.md`.
2. Test **what you changed** plus obvious regressions (don’t full-crawl all lessons).
3. **Fix** confirmed bugs when safe.
4. End the turn with the **QA Report** template from the skill (bugs found + fixed).

Skip the full QA loop only for pure chat questions with no file edits.
